text: FC Stattegg was a women's football club from Stattegg, Austria. The club played in the ÖFB-Frauenliga, the highest class in Austrian women soccer. In 2011 the team was token over by SK Sturm Graz. ==Current squad== as 20 May 2011, in brackets national team ===Goalkeeper=== * Katrin Hermann (Austria U 19) *Lucija Mori (Slovenia) * Celina Ettl ===Defence=== * Julia Seitz * Angelika Alter * Susanne Ehgartner (Austria U 19) * Christina Seitinger * Christina Fischler * Tanja Eibinger * Petra Glavac ===Midfielder=== * Stefanie Brandner * Kerstin Fernitz * Lisa Weissensteiner * Melanie Schweiger * Kerstin Kropf * Alexandra Panait * Verena Söll *Lourdes Cervantes Duenas * Stefanie Hierzer ===Forwards=== * Tanja Altenbacher * Simona Koren (Austria U 19) * Christina Peintinger (Austria U 17, Austria U 19) * Elisabeth Walcher * Deniz Kuyucaklioglu (Austria U 17), on loan from USC Landhaus * Stephanie Schachner ==Other websites== *Official website Category:Austrian football clubs Category:Women's football in Austria Category:Football clubs of Styria Category:2008 establishments in Europe Category:2000s establishments in Austria
